window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Worth isn't given but taken.</b></p> <p>After her 12th birthday, Adelheid von Vuldar must take the next step for her ascension to the throne, the Reginnaglar Ceremony. For generations, members of the imperial family have tested their mettle in dungeons to prove their worthiness, and now, it is Adelheid's turn. Leading her fledging band of knights, Adelheid will delve deep into the Byrgir Dungeon and become one step closer to the throne.</p> <p>But as Adelheid soon discovers, monsters are far from the worse danger within the dungeon.</p>"; 
